---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Chaos With Clarity | AJ"
  description="Short, honest ideas about ego, experience, and being fully alive — for people who think too much and feel even more."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="min-height:100svh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:9rem 3rem 5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#f3e8d8;">

    <div style="position:absolute;right:-5vw;top:8%;width:clamp(220px,40vw,540px);height:clamp(220px,40vw,540px);border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c17f3a,#5d6b45);opacity:0.07;pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:3rem;top:0;bottom:0;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,#cec5ad 20%,#cec5ad 80%,transparent);opacity:0.5;"></div>

    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;width:100%;position:relative;">

      <p style="font-size:0.64rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:400;">Essays · Poetry · Inner Work</p>

      <h1 style="margin-bottom:2.75rem;line-height:0.88;">
        <span style="display:block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Chaos</span>
        <span style="display:block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3.8vw,3.2rem);font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:#c17f3a;padding-left:clamp(1rem,3vw,3rem);line-height:1.5;">With</span>
        <span style="display:block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Clarity</span>
      </h1>

      <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:clamp(0.92rem,1.6vw,1.05rem);max-width:34rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:300;border-left:2px solid #cec5ad;padding-left:1.25rem;">
        Short, honest ideas about ego, experience, and being fully alive.<br/>
        <em style="color:#5d6b45;font-style:italic;">For people who think too much and feel even more.</em>
      </p>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;align-items:center;">
        <a href="/writings" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1a1612;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1612;padding-bottom:3px;font-weight:400;">Read the Latest</a>
        <a href="/join" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7a7260;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;padding-bottom:3px;font-weight:400;">Get the Letters</a>
        <a href="https://calendly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.9rem 1.9rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;">Book Soul + Strategy</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS THIS SPACE -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 3rem 0;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 3fr;gap:0;border:1px solid #cec5ad;" class="what-grid">
      <div style="padding:3rem;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;background:#e8dcc8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;">
        <div>
          <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">What is this?</p>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.2rem);color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:0.01em;">The calm corner of the internet where we slow down, question everything.</h2>
        </div>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.82rem;line-height:1.9;margin-top:2rem;">
          Not ten steps to fix your life. Perspectives that stay with you the next time you're scrolling at 2am, or wondering why you still feel restless even when everything looks fine on paper.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:2rem;font-weight:400;">This space is for you if</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;">
          <li style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:#c17f3a;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">You're tired of empty motivation and want depth without the jargon.</p>
          </li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:#c17f3a;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">You overthink, feel a lot, and secretly like that about yourself.</p>
          </li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:#c17f3a;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">You're curious about mindfulness, but allergic to perfectionism and spiritual performance.</p>
          </li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:#c17f3a;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">You want to own fewer things, carry less ego, and experience more life.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/writings" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;margin-top:2.5rem;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid transparent;transition:border-color 0.2s;">
          Start reading <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LATEST PIECES + POEM -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 3rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr;border:1px solid #cec5ad;" class="home-grid">

      <!-- Latest pieces -->
      <div style="padding:3rem;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;">
        <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:2rem;font-weight:400;">Latest from the Chaos</p>

        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;">

          <a href="/writings" style="display:block;text-decoration:none;padding:1.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;" onmouseover="this.style.paddingLeft='0.5rem'" onmouseout="this.style.paddingLeft='0'" style="transition:padding 0.2s;">
            <p style="font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Essay</p>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:0.4rem;line-height:1.3;">Who Owns You?</h3>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.8;">How our gadgets, purchases, and "rewards" slowly start controlling our thoughts, time, and emotions — and how to take your attention back.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/writings" style="display:block;text-decoration:none;padding:1.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;">
            <p style="font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Essay</p>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:0.4rem;line-height:1.3;">We Were Never Meant for Intelligence</h3>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.8;">Why AI is not the real threat — the real danger is humans forgetting that our edge was experience, not efficiency.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/writings" style="display:block;text-decoration:none;padding:1.5rem 0;">
            <p style="font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Essay</p>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:0.4rem;line-height:1.3;">Choosing Reality Over Symbols</h3>
            <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.8;">How we mistake words, labels, and spoilers for the real thing — and what it means to actually live your own experience.</p>
          </a>

        </div>

        <a href="/writings" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;margin-top:2rem;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;text-decoration:none;">
          All writings <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;">

        <!-- Latest Poem -->
        <div style="padding:2.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;flex:1;"
             data-poem-card
             data-title="Unstruck Silence (Anhat Nad)"
             data-date="March 2026"
             data-poem="There is a sound
that was never struck —
no string plucked, no drum hit,
no throat opened to release it.

It was here before you arrived.
It is here after the last thought
you'll ever think
dissolves.

You have heard it in the space
between two breaths —
not the inhale,
not the exhale,
but the pause that holds both,
the way a door frame holds
a house.

You have heard it in the room
after crying stops,
when the chest finally unclenches
and something older than grief
comes through.

The mystics called it Anahata —
unstruck.
The thing that hums
without cause,
loves without reason,
stays without being asked.

You think you have to earn stillness.
You think silence is the reward
for surviving.

But it is not earned.
It is only uncovered —
the way snow uncovers
ground
by melting."
             data-reflection="Anhat Nad is a concept from Indian classical music and tantra — the sound that was never struck. The Anahata chakra, or heart center, is said to resonate with this unstruck sound. I wrote this after a long meditation session where I kept waiting for something to happen. Nothing did. And then I realized — that was it.">
          <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.25rem;font-weight:400;">Latest Poem</p>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.25rem;color:#1a1612;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:1.25rem;font-weight:500;">Unstruck Silence<br/><span style="font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:1rem;color:#7a7260;">(Anhat Nad)</span></h3>
          <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:0.98rem;line-height:2.1;border-left:2px solid #c17f3a;padding-left:1.1rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
            There is a sound<br/>that was never struck —<br/>no string plucked, no drum hit,<br/>no throat opened.
          </p>
          <button data-open-poem style="background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;padding:0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.6'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">
            Read full <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Join the letters -->
        <div style="padding:2.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:400;">Stay in the Clarity</p>
          <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Honest notes from the middle of it all. No spam, no daily grind tips.</p>
          <form action="/join" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
            <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" style="background:#f3e8d8;border:1px solid #cec5ad;color:#1a1612;font-size:0.85rem;padding:0.75rem 0.9rem;width:100%;outline:none;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:300;" />
            <button type="submit" style="background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.8rem;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:400;">Get the Letters</button>
          </form>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT STRIP -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 7rem;">
    <div style="background:#e8dcc8;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:3rem 3.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
      <div style="position:absolute;right:-2rem;top:-2rem;width:10rem;height:10rem;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid #cec5ad;opacity:0.4;"></div>
      <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">Who writes here</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(1.15rem,2.5vw,1.7rem);color:#1a1612;line-height:1.65;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:0.75rem;font-style:italic;">
        "I'm AJ — a writer and creator who turns the mess of everyday life into lines that make you pause, breathe, and see differently."
      </p>
      <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.9;max-width:42rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Not a guru, therapist, or productivity coach. Just someone who spent a lot of time lost in their own head — and decided to turn that chaos into something useful.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/about" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7a7260;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:0.65rem 1.25rem;font-weight:400;">About AJ →</a>
        <a href="/offerings" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #c17f3a;padding:0.65rem 1.25rem;font-weight:400;">Work with Me →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .what-grid > div:first-child { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #cec5ad; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .home-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .home-grid > div:first-child { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #cec5ad; }
  }
</style>
